      <title>英国股票结算方式转变对英镑交易构成挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/uk-s-t-1-stocks-settlement-shift-poses-challenge-for-pound-trading</link>
      <description><![CDATA[负责领导此次转型的组织表示，鉴于英镑的流动性不如美元，英国跟随美国采用更快的股票交易机制的举措可能会给外汇行业带来挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/uk-s-t-1-stocks-settlement-shift-poses-challenge-for-pound-trading</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 15:05:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通首席执行官戴蒙称美国已变得反对并购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-08/us-has-become-anti-m-a-says-jpmorgan-ceo-dimon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通首席执行官杰米·戴蒙表示，美国已成为“一个反对并购的国家，这是个坏主意”。他说，合并通常是一个好主意，中型银行应该被允许合并。他在伦敦接受了彭博社丽莎·阿布拉莫维茨的采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-08/us-has-become-anti-m-a-says-jpmorgan-ceo-dimon</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 14:55:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Verizon 为收购 Frontier 举债 100 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/verizon-lines-up-10-billion-in-debt-for-frontier-acquisition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Verizon Communications Inc. 已获得 100 亿美元的短期银行资金，用于资助其收购 Frontier Communications Parent Inc.。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/verizon-lines-up-10-billion-in-debt-for-frontier-acquisition</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 14:53:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雷·达里奥 (Ray Dalio) 认为美联储不会进行“大幅”降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/ray-dalio-doesn-t-see-the-fed-making-significant-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在政策制定者将联邦基金利率下调半个百分点后，亿万富翁投资者雷·达利奥 (Ray Dalio) 预计美联储不会“大幅降息”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/ray-dalio-doesn-t-see-the-fed-making-significant-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 14:52:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>优胜美地国家公园为何一片混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-08/why-yosemite-national-park-is-a-mess</link>
      <description><![CDATA[化学品泄漏、设施老化和鼠患使约塞米蒂国家公园的安全受到质疑。员工们将责任归咎于酒店公司 Aramark，该公司表示正在努力清理。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-08/why-yosemite-national-park-is-a-mess</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 14:48:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚连续第二次降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/kenya-cuts-interest-rate-for-second-straight-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于食品和燃料价格上涨放缓，通货膨胀率降至 12 年来的最低水平，肯尼亚央行连续第二次下调基准利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/kenya-cuts-interest-rate-for-second-straight-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 14:23:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
